dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Pacifico Mountain and Palmdale (south half) quadrangles, Los Angeles County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by Helmut E. Ehrenspeck.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights; depths shown by soundings.
"Prepared in cooperation with the U.S. Forest Service, Angeles National Forest; California Dept. of Conservation, Division of Mines and Geology; and the U.S. Geological Survey."
Includes quadrangle location map, and index to sources of geology and topography.
